            After completing this list, you can complete problem 1 from homework 1. 
        </p>
    </subsection>

    <subsection>
        <title>1.2 - What are solutions to differential equations?</title>
        <p>
            In this section, we will learn what solutions to differential equations look like. We will also learn how to verify them and check for intervals of existence. This section satisfies module objectives 4-5. 
